# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# CRAZY CHIPS — Production Environment
# Copy this to .env on your VPS (NOT .env.local)
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

NODE_ENV=production

# ── Database ──────────────────────────────
# Use Neon (free) or your Hostinger managed PostgreSQL
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/crazychips_db

# ── App URL ───────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://yourdomain.com

# ── Auth ──────────────────────────────────
NEXTAUTH_URL=https://yourdomain.com
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=generate-with-openssl-rand-base64-32

# ── Stripe (live keys) ────────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_...
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...

# ── Pusher (EU cluster) ───────────────────
PUSHER_APP_ID=
PUSHER_KEY=
PUSHER_SECRET=
PUSHER_CLUSTER=eu
NEXT_PUBLIC_PUSHER_KEY=
NEXT_PUBLIC_PUSHER_CLUSTER=eu

# ── Cloudinary ────────────────────────────
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=

# ── Upstash Redis ─────────────────────────
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=

# ── Resend (email) ────────────────────────
RESEND_API_KEY=
RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=orders@yourdomain.com

# ── Google OAuth ──────────────────────────
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=

# ── Apple OAuth ───────────────────────────
APPLE_ID=
APPLE_TEAM_ID=
APPLE_PRIVATE_KEY=
APPLE_KEY_ID=
APPLE_SECRET=
